idated Adjusted), '4' (Parent Company Adjusted)\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"同花顺 (THS) iFinD data provider, offering financial data for Chinese and international markets including stocks, securities, funds, bonds, futures, etc. Supports company announcements, intelligent stock screening, industry analysis, market trend prediction, and more, helping users conduct comprehensive financial data analysis and investment decisions.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 654.98,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.877\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"ths_ifind.company_basics.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"iFinD 公司基础信息 (Company Basics)\",\n      \"description\": \"Retrieve the latest (or a specific date) company basics indicators from THS iFinD. Includes company name, industry, comparable/peer companies, concept tags, codes, established date, registration info, main business, and major products.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"codes\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Security codes, comma-separated (max 50), e.g., '300033.SZ,600030.SH'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"date\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Date, format: 'YYYYMMDD'. Use this field to query historical values. Defaults to latest.\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"同花顺 (THS) iFinD data provider, offering financial data for Chinese and international markets including stocks, securities, funds, bonds, futures, etc. Supports company announcements, intelligent stock screening, industry analysis, market trend prediction, and more, helping users conduct comprehensive financial data analysis and investment decisions.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 780.08,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.914\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"ths_ifind.etf_constituents.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"iFinD ETF成分股票列表 (ETF Constituent Stock List)\",\n      \"description\": \"Query the constituent stock list of an ETF from 同花顺 (THS) iFinD database. Returns detailed information about each constituent stock including stock code, name, share quantity, cash substitution flag, subscription/redemption premium ratios and fixed substitution amounts. Useful for analyzing ETF composition and tracking ETF holdings.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"thscode\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"ETF security code, e.g., '510300.SH', '159001.SZ'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"date\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Query date. Supported formats: 'YYYY-MM-DD', 'YYYY/MM/DD', 'YYYYMMDD'. Defaults to today.\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"同花顺 (THS) iFinD data provider, offering financial data for Chinese and international markets including stocks, securities, funds, bonds, futures, etc. Supports company announcements, intelligent stock screening, industry analysis, market trend prediction, and more, helping users conduct comprehensive financial data analysis and investment decisions.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 644.44,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.91\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"eodhd.real_time.retrieve.v1.3b8a5cf8\",\n      \"name\": \"Retrieve Real-Time (Delayed) Stock Prices\",\n      \"description\": \"Fetch real-time price data for a specified cryptocurrency pair.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"symbol\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Stock ticker symbol with exchange suffix (e.g., AAPL.US)\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"fmt\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Response format\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"json\",\n            \"csv\"\n          ]\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"symbol\": \"EUR.FOREX\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Access historical end-of-day stock prices, intraday data, US stock options, and real-time prices with free and advanced plans. EODHD provides financial data for 150,000+ tickers, including stocks, ETFs, funds, and currencies worldwide.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 1093.58,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.948\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  \"search_id\": \"e5aad163-36cd-4b87-aea0-20c2ea299adc\",\n  \"elapsed_time_ms\": 173.21\n}","cwd":"/Users/lynch/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772590521431}}
