red\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Indicator list, multiple indicators separated by commas. Options: 'common' (common indicators), 'all' (all indicators), or custom indicator list. Default is 'all'\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"codes\": \"300033.SZ,600030.SH\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"同花顺 (THS) iFinD data provider, offering financial data for Chinese and international markets including stocks, securities, funds, bonds, futures, etc. Supports company announcements, intelligent stock screening, industry analysis, market trend prediction, and more, helping users conduct comprehensive financial data analysis and investment decisions.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 1667.64,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.887\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"ths_ifind.quotation.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"iFinD 同花顺行情 (历史+实时) (THS Quotation)\",\n      \"description\": \"Query historical and real-time quotation data for securities in the 同花顺 (THS) iFinD database, supporting price, trading volume, turnover ratio, and other indicators for various financial products including stocks, funds, bonds, and futures.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"codes\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Security codes, multiple codes separated by commas (max 50), e.g., '300033.SZ,600030.SH'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"indicators\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Indicator list, comma-separated. Options: 'common' (common indicators), 'all' (all indicators), or custom list. Default is 'all'. Applies to both history and real-time calls.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"startdate\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Start date, formats: 'YY